properties.Text: I curse the day I helped you beef up.
I hope you run out of time because of this dead end.
There's a reason this exit is so well-guarded.\nFor your own sake, stop.
I can't actively stop you.\nYou have to choose to quit here.
Is this room too complicated?\nThe answer is no. I should have made it impossible.
You have the option of not proceeding.
